# BioSense — Memory

## Goals & Tasks

### Project Goals
- Develop a real-time biological data monitoring and analysis system for medical research.
- Implement machine learning algorithms to process large volumes of biological data.
- Create an intuitive user interface for medical professionals.
- Ensure secure storage and transmission of sensitive health data.
- Achieve integration with existing hospital information systems.

### Key Tasks (with Priorities & Deadlines)
| Task | Priority | Deadline | Status |
|------|----------|----------|--------|
| Design data collection module | P0 | after previous milestone | Planned |
| Implement HTTP-based data ingestion | P0 | after previous milestone | Planned |
| Develop ML analysis pipeline (Random Forest) | P0 | after previous milestone | Planned |
| Build React UI with Material-UI | P1 | after previous milestone | Planned |
| Set up MongoDB database schema | P1 | after previous milestone | Planned |
| Conduct security audit & compliance check | P1 | after previous milestone | Planned |
| Perform integration testing with pilot clinics | P2 | after previous milestone | Planned |
| Deploy system to production environment | P2 | after previous milestone | Planned |

## Decision History

### upon approval — Project Initialization
- **Decision:** Created the BioSense project to develop a real-time biological data monitoring and analysis system.
- **Rationale:** Need to structure and process large volumes of biological data for medical research and personalized treatment approaches.
- **Status:** Completed

### after previous milestone — Goals & Objectives Definition
- **Decision:** Defined main project goals: develop machine learning algorithms for biological data analysis, create a user interface for medical professionals, and ensure secure data storage and transmission.
- **Rationale:** Clear definition of goals and tasks is necessary for effective project management and resource allocation.
- **Status:** Completed

### after previous milestone — Technology & Tool Selection
- **Decision:** Selected the following technologies and tools: Python for machine learning algorithms, React for the user interface, and MongoDB for data storage.
- **Rationale:** Choice based on popularity, functionality, and compatibility with existing systems.
